data.description: Mid-Century Modern home in highly desirable Shepherd Forest minutes from Houston  Heights, Downtown CBD, Texas Medical Center, and world-famous Galleria boasts  wooded, oversized corner lot with massive deck/fences. Zoned to award winning HISD schools, this 4/2 is completely updated and open for family living and entertainment. Master bedroom with marble and glass ensuite, galley kitchen with designer tile/granite, original hardwoods and new systems (A/C, tankless, flex pipe plumbing, paint in/out) all combine for mid-century home that incorporates the best of the 1950’s with all the  modern amenities of today.
